00:03:23.940 --> 00:03:26.520
during our lectures to get a
broader audience coming in.

00:03:26.520 --> 00:03:30.080
Our lawyers suggested
that we don't do that.

00:03:30.080 --> 00:03:33.100
And we thought, well, maybe
we could attract more readers

00:03:33.100 --> 00:03:34.610
to our journal
articles if we just

00:03:34.610 --> 00:03:37.950
added a Kardashian
to the author list.

00:03:37.950 --> 00:03:39.900
Again, apparently, you
